      <div id="CheckBreathing">
        <h3>Check Breathing:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Look to see if their chest is rising and falling.</li>
          <li>Listen over their mouth and nose for breathing sounds.</li>
          <li>Feel their breath against your cheek for 10 seconds.</li>
          <li>
            <a href="./videos#CheckBreathing"
